title: Amherst tops readers' prep football rankings
text:
Amherst tops readers' prep football rankings Robert Mentzer , Gannett Wisconsin Media 1:58 p.m. CDT October 6, 2015 Buy Photo Amherst is the No. 1 team in this week's central Wisconsin readers' prep football rankings. (Photo: Megan McCormick/Stevens Point Journal Media) Buy Photo 1 CONNECT 2 TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Our sports reporters each week make their power rankings for central Wisconsin prep football teams . And each week we ask readers to cast their votes for the top teams in the region. (We tally votes each Monday, so cast your votes by the end of the day Sunday for next week.) 
Here in descending order are readers' Central Wisconsin Prep Sports Power Rankings: 
10. D.C. Everest Marathon beat Edgar, 16-8, at Edgar, Friday, October 2, 2015. Dan Young/Gannett Central Wisconsin Media Buy Photo Marathon beat Edgar, 16-8, at Edgar, Friday, October 2, 2015.
